leradas-para-wordpress-y-woocommerce/',4,'portfolio','',0),(733,0,'2026-03-21 20:56:18','2026-03-21 20:56:18','<h2>Overview</h2>\n<p>A suite of commercial WordPress and WooCommerce plugins published on Envato CodeCanyon marketplace. The collection includes tools for social sharing, product recommendations, search optimization, and AMP support — all developed as part of the TeamDev / Custom4Web plugin ecosystem.</p>\n\n<h2>My role</h2>\n<p>Core developer across all plugins in the collection. Architecture, WooCommerce API integration, admin UI, frontend components, and CodeCanyon marketplace publishing and support.</p>\n\n<h2>Plugins in the collection</h2>\n\n<h3>WP AMP — Accelerated Mobile Pages (1,975 sales, $49)</h3>\n<p>The #1 top-selling AMP plugin on CodeCanyon. Full AMP support for WordPress and WooCommerce — pages, posts, products, Google Ads, analytics, and custom AMP templates.</p>\n\n<h3>WooCommerce Related Products C4W (217 sales, $29)</h3>\n<p>Dynamic rules engine for upsell and cross-sell product recommendations. Configurable rules based on categories, tags, attributes, and purchase history to increase average order value.</p>\n\n<h3>Search Manager for WooCommerce & WordPress (152 sales, $19)</h3>\n<p>Enhanced search plugin with relevance tuning, autocomplete, product search filters, and search analytics. Improves the default WordPress/WooCommerce search experience.</p>\n\n<h3>Chat it! — Social Share Buttons (34 sales, $19)</h3>\n<p>Share buttons for Viber, WhatsApp, Telegram, Skype, and Messenger. Lightweight integration for WordPress and WooCommerce with customizable placement and appearance.</p>\n\n<h2>Stack</h2>\n<p>PHP, WordPress Plugin API, WooCommerce, JavaScript, MySQL, REST API, CSS</p>\n\n<h2>Impact</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>2,300+ total sales across the plugin collection on CodeCanyon</li>\n<li>Consistent plugin architecture and quality across all products</li>\n<li>Active maintenance and compatibility updates</li>\n<li>Used by thousands of WordPress and WooCommerce store owners</li>\n</ul>','WooCommerce Plugin Collection — CodeCanyon Marketplace','A collection of 4 commercial plugins on CodeCanyon with 2,300+ total sales. WP AMP (#1 top-selling), WooCommerce Related Products, Search Manager, and Chat it! — all built for WordPress and WooCommerce.','publish','open','closed','','woocommerce-plugin-collection-codecanyon-marketplace','','','2026-03-21 21:06:12','2026-03-21 21:06:12','',0,'http://localhost:8880/portfolio/woocommerce-plugin-collection-codecanyon-marketplace/',6,'portfolio','',0),(734,0,'2026-03-21 20:56:18','2026-03-21 20:56:18','<h2>Overview</h2>\n<p>A suite of commercial WordPress and WooCommerce plugins published on Envato CodeCanyon marketplace under the TeamDev brand. The collection covers affiliate marketing, search functionality, product management, and e-commerce optimization tools.</p>\n\n<h2>My role</h2>\n<p>Core developer across multiple plugins in the collection. Responsible for plugin architecture, WooCommerce API integration, admin interfaces, frontend components, and CodeCanyon marketplace publishing.</p>\n\n<h2>What I built</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Affiliate Links Lite — affiliate link management, cloaking, tracking, and analytics for WooCommerce</li>\n<li>Search Manager Lite — enhanced search functionality with filters, relevance tuning, and WooCommerce product search</li>\n<li>Multiple WooCommerce extensions for product display, cart behavior, and checkout optimization</li>\n<li>Shared plugin framework with consistent settings API, update mechanism, and licensing</li>\n<li>Admin dashboards with analytics, configuration options, and bulk management tools</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Stack</h2>\n<p>PHP, WordPress, WooCommerce, JavaScript, MySQL, REST API, CSS</p>\n\n<h2>Impact</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Multiple commercial plugins generating revenue on CodeCanyon marketplace</li>\n<li>Consistent plugin quality and architecture across the collection</li>\n<li>Used by WooCommerce store owners for affiliate marketing a