'http://localhost:8880/?p=762',0,'revision','',0),(763,0,'2026-03-21 21:06:11','2026-03-21 21:06:11','<h2>Overview</h2>\n<p>WProofreader is a WordPress plugin that adds real-time spelling, grammar, and style checking to any text field in the WordPress admin. It works with Gutenberg, Classic Editor, WooCommerce product descriptions, Yoast SEO fields, and custom post types.</p>\n\n<h2>My role</h2>\n<p>I built this plugin from scratch and continue to develop and maintain it. Full ownership — architecture, WordPress API integration, JavaScript frontend, settings UI, compatibility testing, and release management on wordpress.org.</p>\n\n<h2>What I built</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete WordPress plugin architecture — hooks, filters, settings API, admin UI, and frontend JavaScript integration</li>\n<li>Two proofreading modes: check-as-you-type with inline suggestions and a dialog-based proofread mode</li>\n<li>Deep integration with Gutenberg block editor, Classic Editor (TinyMCE), WooCommerce, and Yoast SEO</li>\n<li>Custom and organization-level dictionaries with REST API synchronization</li>\n<li>Autocorrect and autocomplete functionality</li>\n<li>Multi-language support for 20+ languages with grammar checking</li>\n<li>Settings page with activation, language selection, and customization options</li>\n<li>Compatibility layer supporting WordPress 4.x through 6.x</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Stack</h2>\n<p>PHP, WordPress Plugin API, JavaScript, REST API, CSS</p>\n\n<h2>Impact</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>90,000+ downloads on wordpress.org</li>\n<li>Active installs across thousands of WordPress sites worldwide</li>\n<li>Ongoing development with regular feature releases and compatibility updates</li>\n<li>Used by enterprise customers as part of the Your Company product ecosystem</li>\n</ul>','WProofreader — WordPress Spelling & Grammar Plugin','Built from scratch and actively developing a WordPress plugin with 90K+ downloads. Real-time spell and grammar checking for Gutenberg, Classic Editor, WooCommerce